cs.DS, cs.DM, cs.CG, cs.AI, cs.LG 

This paper deals with algorithms for computing the edit distance between ordered labeled trees, which is a problem in data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). It also involves concepts related to graph theory and combinatorics (cs.DM, cs.CG). The algorithms discussed in the paper have applications in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG).
